From a5cc68f3d63306d0d288f31edfc2ae6ef8ecd887 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mathias Krause <minipli@googlemail.com>
Date: Wed, 26 Jun 2013 23:52:30 +0200
Subject: af_key: fix info leaks in notify messages
Git-commit: a5cc68f3d63306d0d288f31edfc2ae6ef8ecd887
Patch-mainline: v3.10
References: bnc#827749 CVE-2013-2234

key_notify_sa_flush() and key_notify_policy_flush() miss to initialize
the sadb_msg_reserved member of the broadcasted message and thereby
leak 2 bytes of heap memory to listeners. Fix that.

